Applying for what you want to study after matric is always tricky for students, most especially wen it comes to taking courses suitable for their grades.
This AI tool will help in firs calculating the Aps score of the learner
After that, it'll give the total amount and hand out/assign courses they think best suit the student to take.
This not only will help the student in finding the right course, but also avoid taking wrong courses which will result to them either dropping out,
or  course-jumping non stop due to having taken the wrong course. 
